Two-Way ANOVA: Computation

To find the MS:

\text{MS}_{\text{X}} = \frac{\text{SS}_{\text{X}}}{\text{df}_{\text{X}}}

To find the test statistic:

\text{F}_{\text{X}} = \frac{\text{MS}_{\text{X}}}{\text{MS}_{\text{E}}}
